Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Frost/Nixon interview cut
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407gz8
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 Jun 1977
Perils of TV taping. Part of Frost/Nixon TV interview deleted from transmission. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less